data.title: Taurus Model 65
data.text:
Specifications

(1978 - Present)

Type: Revolver

Caliber: .357 Magnum, .38 Special

Weight: 2.13 lbs (0.96 kg) (4" barrel)

Barrel Length: 2.5 in (6.35 cm), 4 in (10.16 cm)

Capacity: 6-round cylinder

Fire Modes: SA/DA
